cu.explanation_en: Setting NG AMF interface IP to unreachable subnet '10.0.0.1' will cause NG interface connection failure and registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: T1a_up timing parameter has inconsistent range [196, 96] where min > max, causing front-haul synchronization failure.
du.explanation_zh: T1a_up 定時參數具有不一致的範圍 [196, 96]，其中最小值 > 最大值，導致前傳同步失敗。
